text: The 1130s was a decade that began on 1 January 1130, and ended on 31 December 1139. It is distinct from the decade known as the 114th decade which began on January 1, 1131 and ended on December 31, 1140. == Events and trends == * Romanesque church at Vezelay has a carving completed * 1130 Innocent II is elected pope * 1139 ** Alphonso I becomes the first king of Portugal ** Second Council of the Lateran Category:1130s
title: 1130s
